<center xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt"><b>Question No. 23--</b></center><b xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">Hon. Larry Bagnell</b>:<a name="Para1341341" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt"></a><p xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">
