  <div>
    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=128856&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">Mr. Tom Lukiwski</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2659000"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Madam Speaker, I ask that all remaining questions be allowed to stand.</div>
</p><A NAME="Int-2658443"></A><a HREF="#Int-2658448"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2658442"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
