    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=129429&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">The Acting Speaker (Ms. Denise Savoie)</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2658439"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;<span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2658550"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_right.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a></span></div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Is that agreed?</div>
