<h2 class="hansardH2" align="center" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">ORAL QUESTIONS<A NAME="OOB-2658725"></A>&nbsp;<a HREF="#OOB-2659264"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="+"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#OOB-2658600"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="-"></a></h2>
<h5 class="hansardH5" align="center" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt"><i>[Oral Questions]</i></h5>
