<h3 class="hansardH3" align="center" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">The Environment<A NAME="SOB-2658891"></A>&nbsp;<a HREF="#SOB-2658900"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="+"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#SOB-2658882"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="-"></a></h3><A NAME="Int-2658890"></A><a HREF="#Int-2658893"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2658888"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
