  <div>
    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=128716&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">Hon. Rob Merrifield (Minister of State (Transport), CPC)</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2658937"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr. Speaker, we are not compromising the environment in any way. We are getting infrastructure dollars working for Canadians and Canadians working right now. </div>
</p><a name="Para1341605" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt"></a><p xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">
