  <div>
    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=128709&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">Hon. Gail Shea (Minister of Fisheries and Oceans, CPC)</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2658955"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;<span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2658962"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_right.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a></span></div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr. Speaker, on any application, extenuating circumstances must be taken into account. Licensing decisions are confidential matters.</div>
</p><A NAME="Int-2658960"></A><a HREF="#Int-2658962"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2658958"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
