<h3 class="hansardH3" align="center" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">International Trade<A NAME="SOB-2658979"></A>&nbsp;<a HREF="#SOB-2658986"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="+"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#SOB-2658965"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="-"></a></h3><A NAME="Int-2658978"></A><a HREF="#Int-2658981"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2658974"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
