    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=128523&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">Mr. Rodger Cuzner (Cape Breton—Canso, Lib.)</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2658428"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;<span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2660419"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_right.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a></span></div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Mr. Speaker, on behalf of our party and caucus, we believe the Speaker is a great Canadian.</div>
</p><A NAME="Int-2659094"></A><a HREF="#Int-2659095"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2659093"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
