<p align="center" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">Oral Questions<A NAME="SOBQ-2660454"></A>&nbsp;<a HREF="#SOBQ-2660516"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="+"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#SOBQ-2659022"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="-"></a></p><A NAME="Int-2659095"></A><a HREF="#Int-2659331"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2659094"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
