  <div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I would like to inform the parliamentary secretary that I gave very substantial, comprehensive input to the minister on the budget. So I would like to ask for an apology. He could either give it in the House or in writing. I do not want to make a big deal of it, but I did due diligence for my constituents and put in a lot of suggestions.</div>
</p><A NAME="Int-2659331"></A><a HREF="#Int-2659096"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2659095"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
