        <a name="Para1341751" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt"></a><p xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">
  <div>
    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=128909&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">The Speaker</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2659094"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;<span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2659096"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_right.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a></span></div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I am sure the hon. member for <A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=128784&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">Yukon</A> knows it is really a point of debate, not a point of order, but he has made his point.</div>
</p>
<p align="center" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*</p>
<h3 class="hansardH3" align="center" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">Message from the Senate<A NAME="SOB-2659098"></A>&nbsp;<a HREF="#SOB-2659285"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="+"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#SOB-2659022"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="-"></a></h3><A NAME="Int-2659096"></A><a HREF="#Int-2659539"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2659331"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
            [<a class="toc" href="javascript:void(0);" OnClick="JumpToTOC('2659096')">Table of Contents</a>]
        <a name="Para1341752" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt"></a><p xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">
  <div>
    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=128909&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">The Speaker</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2659331"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;<span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2659539"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_right.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a></span></div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;I have the honour to inform the House that a message has been received from the Senate, informing this House that the Senate has passed the following public bill to which the concurrence of this House has desired:</div>
