  <div>
    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=129035&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">The Acting Speaker (Ms. Denise Savoie)</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2658982"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Question and comments, the hon. member for Hochelaga.</div>
</p>
<p xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">[<i>Translation</i>]</p><A NAME="Int-2659280"></A><a HREF="#Int-2659291"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_down.gif" border="0" alt="next intervention"></a>&nbsp;<a HREF="#Int-2659278"><IMG SRC="/common/images/arrow2_up.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
