        <a name="Para1341892" xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt"></a><p xmlns:msxsl="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:xslt">
  <div>
    <div><b><A class="WebOption" HREF="/HousePublications/GetWebOptionsCallBack.aspx?SourceSystem=PRISM&amp;ResourceType=Affiliation&amp;ResourceID=128175&amp;language=1&amp;DisplayMode=2">Hon. Dominic LeBlanc</A>: </b><span class="nextIntervention"><a class="nav_link" href="#Int-2659525"><img src="/common/images/arrow2_left.gif" border="0" alt="previous intervention"></a></span>&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Then I suppose, Madam Speaker, that I shall have to be brief.</div>
